Compiling & Installing Hashit
=============================

./0
make
su -c 'make install'

This will install hashit in /usr/local. The 0 configuration scripts allow you
to change installation directories Type './0 --help' for info about all
options.

hashit includes a pkg-config file, so then you only need to use the
pkg-config utility in the usual way to link you binary to hashit.


